algebraic tensors a, b, ..., which may be Ket, Pauli, or any other \
NonCommutative species. CircleTimes[m1, m2, ...] returns the direct product \
of matrices m1, m2, .... CircleTimes[v1, v2, ...] returns the direct product \
of vectors (one-dimensional arrays) v1, v2, .... The result is a \
